# Day 32 - Marketing Strategy Simulator

## Objective

Build an AI-powered Marketing Strategy Simulator that helps businesses and personal brands create effective marketing plans through interactive decision-making.

---

## Features

- Business Mode
- Personal Brand Mode
- Random Client Mode
- Target Audience Analysis
- Marketing Platform Selection
- Content Pillar Planning
- 30-Day Marketing Roadmap
- Marketing Event Simulation
- Growth Report
- Reusable Claude Prompts

---

## Workflow

1. Started the simulator.
2. Selected Business / Personal Brand / Random Client mode.
3. Reviewed the target audience.
4. Selected the best marketing platforms.
5. Chose three content pillars.
6. Generated a 30-day marketing roadmap.
7. Responded to a randomized marketing event.
8. Reviewed the final Growth Report.
9. Explored reusable Claude prompts.
10. Tested multiple scenarios.

